TITLE: Combining Multiple Validation Sources in Vue with Formwerk
DESCRIPTION: This snippet showcases how to combine HTML constraints, field-level schema, and form-level schema validation in a single form. It demonstrates the cascading validation behavior in Formwerk.
SOURCE: https://github.com/formwerkjs/formwerk.dev/blob/main/src/content/docs/guides/forms/index.mdx#2025-04-13_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: vue
CODE:
